{"text_id":118480,"tokens":["In"," recent"," years"," there"," has"," been"," much"," debate"," over"," whether"," students"," can"," bring"," their"," mobile"," phones"," into"," school"," grounds"," at"," all",".","  ","Some"," argue"," against"," allowing"," them"," because"," it"," distra","cts"," from"," learning"," while"," others"," believe"," they"," are"," useful"," tools"," for"," communication"," between"," teachers"," and"," parents"," as"," well"," as"," among"," classmates"," themselves",".","   ","This"," paper"," will"," examine"," both"," sides"," of"," this"," argument"," before"," making"," its"," own"," recommendation"," based"," upon"," research"," conducted"," by"," other"," scholars"," who"," have"," studied"," similar"," issues",".","    ","The"," first"," section"," examines"," the"," pros"," and"," cons"," associated"," with"," using"," mobile"," devices"," such"," as"," smart"," phones"," within"," educational"," settings",".","   ","It"," is"," argued"," here"," that"," although"," these"," devices"," may"," be"," beneficial"," when"," used"," appropriately"," (","e",".","g",".,"," texting"," homework"," questions","),"," they"," also"," pose"," significant"," risks"," if"," allowed"," unrestricted"," access"," throughout"," the"," day",".","   ","For"," example",","," some"," studies"," suggest"," that"," excessive"," time"," spent"," online"," via"," smartphones"," leads"," to"," lower"," grades"," due"," to"," decreased"," attention"," spans"," caused"," by"," frequent"," interruptions"," from"," incoming"," messages"," and","/","or"," notifications",".","   ","In"," addition",",..."," [...]"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"bloomz","label":1}